  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study was a survey of drug users who obtain buprenorphine from the black market and have
      used buprenorphine during the last month. Subjects were surveyed at various locations
      (streets, railway stations, etc.) with a few simple questions in order to describe the use of
      buprenorphine in this &quot;out of care&quot; population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Participants were found from various places and using a &quot;snow ball&quot; technique.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
